pr_title: [mitmweb] Add "one click resume / accept all" button
pr_body:
#### Description

When we want to intercept a flow and forward it in mitmweb, we have to select the intercepted flow in the flow view and push the resume button.
I implemented "one click resume button" and "accept all" button.
We just have to push button once to forward intercepted flows.


#### Checklist

 - [x] I have updated tests where applicable.
 - [x] I have added an entry to the CHANGELOG.

#### Description
